OL,3,CFormula 1 champion Lando Norris having
OL,4,Chis own Madame Tussauds waxwork
OL,6,FFormula 1 World Champion Lando Norris
OL,7,Fhas said it is going to be "surreal"
OL,8,Fhaving a waxwork figure of himself
OL,9,Fappear at Madame Tussauds in London.
OL,11,FThe McLaren driver, 26, has been
OL,12,Fworking with the attraction's studio
OL,13,Fteam to create the waxwork.
OL,15,FBorn in Bristol and raised in
OL,16,FGlastonbury, Norris burst onto the
OL,17,FFormula 1 scene in 2019 and notched up
OL,18,Fhis first World Drivers' Championship
OL,19,Ftitle secured December 2025
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
