PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1774019480
OL,3,CFormula 1 champion Lando Norris having
OL,4,Chis own Madame Tussauds waxwork
OL,6,FHe said: "It's pretty surreal to think
OL,7,FI'll have a figure in Madame Tussauds,
OL,8,Fit's such a big honour.
OL,10,F"Working with the artists has been
OL,11,Fawesome, and seeing all the detail
OL,12,Fthey've put into the figure is really
OL,13,Fimpressive. I can't wait for fans to
OL,14,Fcome and see the finished figure in
OL,15,FLondon this summer."
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUwD@TO]
