PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1774019480
OL,3,CFormula 1 champion Lando Norris having
OL,4,Chis own Madame Tussauds waxwork
OL,6,FSteve Blackburn, General Manager at
OL,7,FMadame Tussauds London said: "Lando
OL,8,FNorris is firmly at the forefront of
OL,9,Fmodern sport and culture, ambitious,
OL,10,Ffearless and hugely popular with fans
OL,11,Faround the world.
OL,13,F"From the moment we started working
OL,14,Fwith Lando, it was clear we were
OL,15,Fcreating something really special, and
OL,16,Four team has been working at full
OL,17,Fthrottle to ensure an exact likeness.
OL,19,F"He's been fantastic throughout the
OL,20,Fprocess, patiently sitting still and
OL,21,Fnot racing around as usual!"
OL,26,@oD@^OUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@\O]
